    public class SyncCustomResourcesResponse
extends SiperianResponse
    Returns UIDs of custom resources that were added, deleted or left unchanged in the Hub database, resulting from a SyncCustomResourcesRequest. The UIDs that were added or left unchanged can be used in GetResourcePrivilegesRequest API calls.

    Note, the UIDs returned will be fully qualified even if they were partially qualified in the request.
